data.description: Discover the ideal blend of comfort and convenience in this charming single-family home. Boasting four spacious bedrooms and a stylish 1.5 baths, this residence offers a welcoming open layout perfect for modern living. Enjoy the ease of parking with ample space available. Situated near a bustling shopping mall and major highways connecting to NYC, this home provides the ultimate in accessibility without compromising on comfort or style
